{"tid":1536291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《手足情》4／9 至7／9係休息期","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:41.000Z","uid":8948,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2b7d18ef091bf30e97d788b873ef89bf068c9024","tid":1536291,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:21:41.000Z","msg":"八月尾九月頭接連都有唔同活動＋集會<br />\n不論係前線，後勤，文宣，和理非都過左好多晚痛心既無眠夜，<br />\n無數既負面資訊排山倒海咁湧入腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係時候抖一抖，回一回氣<br />\n保持抗爭力量，休息係好重要既一環<br />\n我建議黎緊每個weekend 都只需要keep住一次大型活動<br />\n其餘飯後活動就因各區而異，但大前提係不被捕，保持抗爭人數<br />\n<br />\n首先用10分鐘照顧一下自己心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/%E7%94%A8-10-%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E7%85%A7%E9%A1%A7%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/444597819473358/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F%25E7%2594%25A8-10-%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E7%2585%25A7%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%2F444597819473358%2F&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vuDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=289310d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/%E7%94%A8-10-%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E7%85%A7%E9%A1%A7%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/444597819473358/</a><br />\n<br />\n嘗試擺低所有新聞，做一啲自己好耐冇做既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靜靜地飲杯咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇返甩左好耐既劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，去戲院睇返套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同朋友食個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，見下女男朋友（如果有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），睇下女優有冇新片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等等<br />\n<br />\n然後每晚十點鐘就將所有憤怒化為行動，十點鐘對窗大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qrpi8cy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQrpi8cy.jpg&h=97148ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>休息不是遺忘，是為了一起走下去。<br />\n<br />\n香港人！加油！贏就一齊贏，輸就一齊輸，一個都不能少！<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vuDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=a1dd78c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n同意請正評推post"},{"pid":"3b18580f3e684d5e7e27ac03d993017fe7571da2","tid":1536291,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:21:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a938050d7ecfb47667c9b28cfbbaae436f52edc8","tid":1536291,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"26995fe450f913ead7ba7995fbd96a5be0e0440b","tid":1536291,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"8aacac87db6cc155a0ffd09b340c9cd875615fb5","tid":1536291,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:23:22.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"e1465c15483777b00676f553fd2149dece5b4cbd","tid":1536291,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:23:33.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"197cfaa4d160ee99e8c1638311acf19fe6c14f8f","tid":1536291,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:23:43.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推"},{"pid":"332285d94d7b10a3fe5e3ab3787f95cca243840c","tid":1536291,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"02617b7b842092b9e9113ca29483adc3685647b6","tid":1536291,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:25:34.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"deec1b4927c6064b69b13b50a1046b9ff7ad8c3c","tid":1536291,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:51:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83090894a81a72d0d87c075f906870c49612450e","tid":1536291,"uid":8948,"lik